e invariance and shape fidelity, significantly improving performance in downstream tasks such as category-level retrieval, few-shot reconstruction, and generative modeling. Our method advances the state-of-the-art by replacing rigid geometric priors with learned functional canonicalization, offering superior robustness to orientation variation across both symmetric and asymmetric object classes.",
